#GDG_Ismailia
#WTMIsmailia
#IWD2018
-----------------------------------------------------------------
All of us as girls faced the moments of frustration and failure in reaching our dream, but it is natural that we pass those moments and our community have a famous saying that " girl doesn't have anything except her husband house".

But the fact reverses that girls every day make tangible achievements in various fields around the world, so on March 8 of each year, the world celebrates the International Women's Day.

And we are in GDG Ismailia interested in helping you reach your dream and we will always be with you in that way. so this year we are responsible for organizing international women day event in the Canal cities which will be held in Ismailia, we will try to present new thoughts for girls to succeed in technology and business.

During the day of the event, we will provide sessions & workshop & talks about technology and business, real success stories of Ismailia's girls, full of hope and new thinking.

Book your seat with us by joining our meetup channel https://goo.gl/ivFQQS Stay tuned and follow our event.

DevFest Egypt is a developer-focused community-driven conference hosted annually in Cairo, Egypt.

DevFest Egypt is a non-profit event, and attendance is free for confirmed applicants.

The aim of DevFest Egypt is to provide a place for professional and hobbyist developers, and all working in the software industry in Egypt, to hear about new topics so that they can take that and continue learning and advancing their skills.

Think of DevFest as an event where attendees get to be with the community to learn, network and get inspired regardless of gender, sexual orientation, disabilities, neurodiversity, physical appearance, body size, ethnicity, nationality, race, age, religion, experience level, technology and programming knowledge or the language of choice.

Expect tech talks on #Android, #Google #Assistant, #Flutter, #Machine_Learning, #PWA and #Cloud tech.
